msgid "About"
msgstr "Quant a "

msgid "Close"
msgstr "Tanca"

msgid "Help"
msgstr "Ajuda "

msgid "OK"
msgstr "D'acord"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The user clicks the "Save List" button to save the list of packages
#. installed by the user.
msgid "Save List"
msgstr "Desa la llista"

msgid "Changelog"
msgstr "Registre de canvis"

msgid "License"
msgstr "Llicència"

msgid "MX User Installed Packages"
msgstr "MX User Installed Packages"

msgid "About MX User Installed Packages"
msgstr "Quant a MX User Installed Packages"

msgid "An app to list and re-install user installed packages."
msgstr ""
"Una aplicació per llistar i reinstal·lar paquets instal·lats per l'usuari."

msgid "MX User Installed Packages Changelog"
msgstr "Registre de canvis de MX User Installed Packages"

msgid "Date:"
msgstr "Data:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The hostname of the system.
msgid "Host:"
msgstr "Amfitrió:"

msgid "System:"
msgstr "Sistema:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The packages installed by the user (UIP).
#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The desktop entry name will be displayed within the menu.
msgid "User Installed Packages"
msgstr "Paquets instal·lats per l'usuari"

msgid "Package name"
msgstr "Nom del paquet"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripció "

msgid "List of user installed packages"
msgstr "Llista dels paquets instal·lats per l'usuari"

msgid "List of unavailable packages"
msgstr "Llista dels paquets no disponibles"

msgid "The following packages are not available or cannot be installed:"
msgstr "Aquests paquets no estan disponibles o no es poden instal·lar:"

msgid "MX - User Installed Packages"
msgstr "MX - User Installed Packages"

msgid ""
"This app is designed to make it easy to reinstall packages that the user has"
" added to the default installation and retained."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta aplicació té la finalitat de facilitar la reinstal·lació dels "
"paquets afegits per l'usuari a una instal·lació per omissió i retinguts."

msgid "It combines two steps:"
msgstr "Combina dos passos:"

msgid "1) quickly and easily create a list of those packages"
msgstr "1) crea ràpida i fàcilment una llista d'aquests paquets"

msgid ""
"2) use that list in another location to review and reinstall those packages,"
" if still available"
msgstr ""
"2) usa aquesta llista en una altra ubicació per revisar i instal·lar aquests"
" paquets, si encara estan disponibles"

msgid "Create a list of user installed packages"
msgstr "Crea una llista dels paquets instal·lats per l'usuari"

msgid "Open a previously saved list and install selected packages"
msgstr ""
"Obre una llista prèviament desada i instal·la els paquets seleccionats"

msgid "You have no packages installed!"
msgstr "No hi ha paquets instal·lats!"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. There may be more than one sentence that needs to be translated.
#. If so, click the tabs with "1" ... "other" to translate them.
#. Do keep the count placeholder "%d".
msgid "You have installed 1 package:"
msgid_plural "You have installed %d packages:"
msgstr[0] "Heu instal·lat 1 paquet:"
msgstr[1] "Heu instal·lat %d paquets:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The list of user installed packages (UIP) failed to save.
msgid "The UIP list of packages installed by the user could not be saved"
msgstr "No puc desar la llista UIP de paquets instal·lats per l'usuari"

msgid "No file selected."
msgstr "No s'ha triat cap fitxer."

msgid "Select which packages you want to install:"
msgstr "Escolliu quins paquets voleu instal·lar:"

msgid "Install packages"
msgstr "Instal·la paquets"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Shown in a progress dialog while checking which packages from the user's
#. list are available.
msgid "Please wait, checking package availability ..."
msgstr "Espereu, si us plau; comprovant la disponibilitat dels paquets..."

msgid "Missing Packages"
msgstr "Paquets absents"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The list of missing packages was saved under:
msgid "[OK] UIP list of missing packages saved:"
msgstr "[D'acord] Llista UIP de paquets absents desada:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The list of missing packages failed to save.
msgid "UIP list of missing packages could not be saved."
msgstr "No puc desar la llista UIP de paquets absents."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Shown in a terminal window after package installation finishes.
#. The user presses Enter to close the terminal.
msgid "Press Enter to exit"
msgstr "Premeu Retorn per sortir"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Header shown in a terminal window that opens to install packages.
#. 'authenticate' means the user must enter their password (sudo/pkexec).
msgid "Installing selected packages, please authenticate"
msgstr "S'instal·len els paquets seleccionats. Si us plau, autentiqueu-vos."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The package cache is the local database of available software packages,
#. refreshed by 'apt update'.
msgid "The package cache is empty."
msgstr "La memòria cau de paquets està buida."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. %d is the number of days since the package cache was last refreshed.
#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The package cache is the local database of available software packages,
#. refreshed by 'apt update'.
#. There may be more than one sentence that needs to be translated.
#. If so, click the tabs with "1" ... "other" to translate them.
#. Do keep the count placeholder "%d" -- it will be replaced by the number of
#. days.
msgid "The package cache has not been refreshed for %d day."
msgid_plural "The package cache has not been refreshed for %d days."
msgstr[0] "La memòria cau de paquets no s'ha refrescat des de fa %d dia."
msgstr[1] "La memòria cau de paquets no s'ha refrescat des de fa %d dies."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. CLI prompt asking whether to run apt update now.
msgid "Update now?"
msgstr "Actualitzo ara?"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Shown after 'apt update' fails (e.g. no internet connection).
msgid ""
"Package cache update failed. Check your internet connection or APT sources "
"lists."
msgstr ""
"L'actualització de la memòria cau de paquets ha fallat. Comproveu la "
"connexió a internet o les llistes de fonts d'APT."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. CLI prompt asking whether to continue despite apt update failure.
msgid "Continue anyway?"
msgstr "Continua igualment?"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Title of a warning dialog shown when the local package database (package
#. cache) is empty or outdated.
#. The package cache is refreshed by running 'apt update'.
msgid "Package Cache Warning"
msgstr "Avís de la Memòria Cau de paquets"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Button in the Package Cache Warning dialog.
#. Runs 'apt update' to refresh the local package database.
msgid "Update Now"
msgstr "Actualitza ara"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Button in the Package Cache Warning dialog.
#. Skips the package database update and proceeds with installation.
msgid "Continue Anyway"
msgstr "Continua igualment"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The package cache is the local database of available software packages,
#. refreshed by 'apt update'.
#. APT_UPDATE is a placeholder for the command "apt update" -- do not
#. translate or change it.
msgid "Run APT_UPDATE now to refresh the package cache?"
msgstr "Executo APT_UPDATE ara per refrescar la Memòria Cau de paquets?"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The package cache is the local database of available software packages,
#. refreshed by 'apt update'.
msgid "The package cache may be outdated."
msgstr "La memòria cau de paquets pot haver caducat."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Header shown in a terminal window that opens to run 'apt update'.
#. 'authenticate' means the user must enter their password (sudo/pkexec).
msgid "Updating package cache, please authenticate"
msgstr "Actualitzant la memòria cau de paquets, si us plau autentiqueu"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Shown in a terminal window after 'apt update' finishes.
#. The user presses Enter to close the terminal and return to the app.
msgid "Press Enter to continue"
msgstr "Premeu Retorn per continuar"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The user selects a file to save the list of user installed packages (UIP).
msgid "Select location to save file"
msgstr "Trieu la ubicació per desar el fitxer"

msgid "File exists. Overwrite?"
msgstr "El fitxer ja hi és. El voleu sobreescriure? "

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The list of user installed packages (UIP) was saved successfully under:
msgid "[OK] UIP list saved:"
msgstr "[D'acord] Llista UIP desada:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The list of user installed packages (UIP) failed to save.
msgid "UIP-list save file failed:"
msgstr "Ha fallat en desar el fitxer de la llista UIP:"

msgid "[ERROR]"
msgstr "[ERROR]"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The user selects a file with user installed packages (UIP) to be read.
msgid "Select UIP list to load"
msgstr "Escolliu la llista UIP a carregar"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The selected file appears not to be a valid list of user installed packages
#. (UIP).
msgid "Not a valid UIP-list file:"
msgstr "No és un fitxer vàlid de llista UIP:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The selected file is directory not a regular file.
msgid "Selected file is a directory."
msgstr "El fitxer triat és un directori."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The selected file is not a regular (text) file.
msgid "Not a regular file"
msgstr "No és un fitxer normal"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The selected file is not readable file.
msgid "File is not readable."
msgstr "No es pot llegir el fitxer."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The type of the file the user has selected: "file type"
msgid "file type"
msgstr "tipus de fitxer"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The selected file is not a plain ASCII text file.
msgid "Not a plain ASCII text file"
msgstr "No és un fitxer ASCII de text net"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The selected file is not a text file.
msgid "Not a text file"
msgstr "No és un fitxer de text"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. UIP = "User Installed Packages".
#. The selected file is not a valid UIP-list file with invalid package names.
msgid "File contains invalid package names"
msgstr "El fitxer conté noms de paquet no vàlids"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The selected file seems not to hold any package names.
msgid "File contains no package names"
msgstr "El fitxer no conté noms de paquet"

msgid "Select a file"
msgstr "Trieu un fitxer"

msgid "Usage:"
msgstr "Ús:"

#. TRANSLATORS: 'command' is a syntax placeholder meaning "one of the commands
#. listed below"
msgid "command"
msgstr "ordre"

#. TRANSLATORS: '[options]' is a syntax placeholder meaning optional flags;
#. keep the square brackets
msgid "[options]"
msgstr "[opcions]"

#. TRANSLATORS: Section header for the list of available commands
msgid "Commands:"
msgstr "Ordres: "

#. TRANSLATORS: CLI (command line interface) mode means the program runs in
#. the terminal without a graphical window; --cli is the literal flag name, do
#. not translate it
msgid "Force CLI mode"
msgstr "Força el mode de línia d'ordres"

msgid "Show this help"
msgstr "Mostra l'ajuda"

msgid "Show version"
msgstr "Mostra la versió"

#. TRANSLATORS: Section header for the list of available options/flags
msgid "Options:"
msgstr "Opcions:"

#. TRANSLATORS: --generate and --install are literal flag names, do not
#. translate them; a single dash (-) means write to standard output instead of
#. a file
msgid "File to write (--generate) or read (--install); use - for stdout"
msgstr ""
"Fitxer a escriure (--generate) o llegir (--install); useu - per stdout"

#. TRANSLATORS: "current dir" means the folder the program was launched from
msgid "Output directory for saved files (default: current dir)"
msgstr "Directori de sortida pels fitxers desats (per omissió: dir. actual)"

#. TRANSLATORS: %s is the directory path.
msgid "Output directory does not exist: %s"
msgstr "No existeix el directori de sortida: %s"

#. TRANSLATORS: %s is the file path.
msgid "File already exists, will not overwrite: %s"
msgstr "El fitxer ja hi és, no el sobreescriuré: %s"

#. TRANSLATORS: %d is the number of packages saved.
msgid "Saved %d package to:"
msgid_plural "Saved %d packages to:"
msgstr[0] "S'han desat %d paquets a:"
msgstr[1] "S'han desat %dpaquets a:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The specified file does not exist. %s is the file path.
msgid "File not found"
msgstr "No trobo el fitxer"

#. TRANSLATORS: %s is the file path.
msgid "No packages found in: %s"
msgstr "No he trobat paquets a: %s"

#. TRANSLATORS: %d is the number of packages being checked.
msgid "Checking availability of %d package..."
msgid_plural "Checking availability of %d packages..."
msgstr[0] "Comprovant la disponibilitat de%d paquets..."
msgstr[1] "Comprovant la disponibilitat de %d paquets..."

#. TRANSLATORS: %d is the number of unavailable packages.
msgid "%d package not available:"
msgid_plural "%d packages not available:"
msgstr[0] "%d paquets no disponibles:"
msgstr[1] "%d paquets no disponibles:"

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. CLI prompt asking whether to save the list of unavailable packages to a
#. file.
msgid "Save missing packages list?"
msgstr "Deso la llista de paquets absents?"

#. TRANSLATORS: %s is the file path.
msgid "Missing packages list saved to: %s"
msgstr "Llista de paquets absents desada a: %s"

msgid "No packages available to install."
msgstr "No hi ha paquets disponibles per instal·lar."

#. TRANSLATORS: %d is the number of packages being installed.
msgid "Installing %d package..."
msgid_plural "Installing %d packages..."
msgstr[0] "Instal·lant %d paquets..."
msgstr[1] "Instal·lant %d paquets..."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. The desktop entry comment will be shown within the menu.
msgid "List user installed packages. Install packages from existing list."
msgstr ""
"Llista paquets instal·lats per l'usuari. Instal·la paquets de la llista."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. Keywords to search in the menu. Hint: Add translated keywords to existing.
msgid "apt;install;package;uip;"
msgstr "apt;install;package;uip;paquet;"

msgid "Authentication is required to install selected packages"
msgstr "Cal autenticar-se per instal·lar els paquets seleccionats"

msgid "Install selected packages"
msgstr "Instal·la els paquets seleccionats"

msgid "Authentication is required to update the package cache"
msgstr "Cal autenticar-se per actualitzar la memòria cau de paquets"

msgid "Update package cache"
msgstr "Actualització de la memòria cau de paquets"
